title: [Southwestern Branch]
description: Crowned in a small dome, the lobby is a nexus for multiple banks and collection offices.  A central archway heads eastward towards the central entry, while the northern and southern walls are a hive of arches.  Pendant lanterns issue a steady white glow, keeping the space free shadows and brightly illuminated.  Cushioned in velveteen, a series of seats encircle a potted blooming canver tree.
paths: Obvious exits: north, northeast, east, southeast, south, west, northwest
